{"tid":719283,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"AI機械人與特首對話　稱身為土生土長香港人感驕傲","createTime":"2018-06-27T10:00:03.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-28T12:38:05.000Z","uid":184679,"like":150,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":25,"replies":[{"pid":"3ededc5191ae737665b60aa4d772b553a28c0b2e","tid":719283,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-27T10:00:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://newsstatic.rthk.hk/images/mfile_1403879_1_L_20180627153941.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnewsstatic.rthk.hk%2Fimages%2Fmfile_1403879_1_L_20180627153941.jpg&h=19f5efdb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n論壇期間，林鄭月娥與人工智能機械人對話。（楊凱力攝）<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n行政長官林鄭月娥出席一個以智慧城市為主題的論壇，她表示，政府去年已發表智慧城市藍圖，未來會積極發展大數據、雲端平台、5G網絡等，亦會著重在生物科技與人工智能兩方面的發展。<br />\n<br />\n論壇期間，林鄭月娥與由香港科技公司研發的人工智能機械人對話。林鄭月娥問對方，如何看香港作為一個智慧城市，機械人回應指，香港在智慧城市的發展仍處於起步階段，預計未來會有更好的發展。機械人又說，對於作為一個土生土長的「香港人」，感到十分驕傲。 <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1403879-20180627.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1403879-20180627.htm&d=mQW3N00r1XXfZyNZcpRAQJ4f2li5K%2Fs6EGgmwhpeblA%3D&h=e594be69\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1403879-20180627.htm&h=402344d1\" target=\"_blank\">http://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1403879-20180627.htm</a><br />\n<br />\n究竟邊個先係機械人?<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9ba8e937c35a8983c2dcddc9b40583a61c41ce4f","tid":719283,"uid":77196,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-27T10:21:31.000Z","msg":"快d失控之後...<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/censored.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/censored.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/censored.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ef5054914b5d024ad033c7faca79c82f0a0e1611","tid":719283,"uid":34103,"like":2,"dislike":85,"score":-83,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-06-27T1